Ingredients:
    Chicken Breast x1
    Chili Pepper 3g
    Salt 3g
    Green Pepper x1
    Parsley x1
    Lemon x1
    Onion x1
Steps:
    Take a Chicken Breast and Season with
        Salt 3g
        Chili Pepper 3g

    Slice
        Chicken Breast x1(Gives Chicken Skewers)
        Lemon x1(Gives Lemon Slices)
        Tomato x1(Gives Tomato Slices
        Onion x1(Gives Onion Slices)

    Take a Skewer an attach to it
        Chicken Skewers x4
        Lemon x2

    Bake Lemon Skewers in Oven

    Grill
        Green Pepper x1
        Onion Slices x1
        Tomato Slices x1

    Transfer to Plate
        Detach Lemon Skewers on to Plate
        Green Pepper  x1
        Parsley Piece x1
        Onion Slices x1
        Tomato Slices x1

    Serve Hot